/*
 *	Linux NET3:	Internet Group Management Protocol  [IGMP]
 *
 *	Authors:
 *		Alan Cox <alan@lxorguk.ukuu.org.uk>
 *
 *	Extended to talk the BSD extended IGMP protocol of mrouted 3.6
 *
